Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.util.stats

Class Summary
Bin The results associated with a single bin.
BinningResult The result of a binning operation including mean observations (with averages and confidence intervals per bin), magnitude bins, and analysis of variance results (F-test, p-value).
DescStats Descriptive statistics functions for observations.
PhaseCalcs This class contains static methods for phase calculations.
